## Design Token Architecture

Two-layer system: **Primitive → Semantic**. Never use Primitive tokens in component files.

## Cross-Platform Conventions

- Feature naming: PascalCase on all platforms
- Routes: kebab-case (web) → PascalCase (iOS/Android)
- All screens on all platforms unless marked platform-specific
